---
title: Szechuan Glazed Duck Breast Donburi with Pickled Carrot and Garlic Jasmine Rice
description: Inspired by some of the world's most popular street food, this tasty Szechuan Glazed Duck Breast Donburi is perfect for a casual sharing-style dinner.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R29_W19_UK_SPR19873-4_Main_1_R_high-0a68ed05.jpg
